                <note rend="inline" type="source">438.00/264: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The High Commissioner in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Russell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-06-15T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 15, 1923—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 7:24 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>82. Department’s 62, May 28, 5 p.m. Haitian Government agrees to limiting
                    jurisdiction of Claims Commission to claims arising before May 3d, 1916.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
